@SAUS3  

Yes, though it would be more accurate to say 'You will never *topdeck* a land again. If you drew a land with [Faithless Looting](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Faithless Looting), for instance, you could still choose to keep and play a land.  

Of course red draw is at a super premium, but it's just to say you could still technically get lands without having to resort to specialized answers like [Crucible of Worlds](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Crucible of Worlds).
